Since Gazebo Classic transitioned to Gazebo Sim the World,Model and Sensor are now called "System"
See all plugins in in the Gazebo Docs
More so since the transition Gazebo has created it's own Topics that are no longer using DDS as a way to communicate Topics. In order to use the Gazebo topics. We need a other program called "ros_gz_bridge", which translates Gazebo topics into ROS topics.
